            "tactics": "The Strider is a flexible multipurpose unit that can swap between two kits, each more effective at different range bands. Use this flexibility to choose the right tool for the job as circumstances change during combat. The Strider lacks the specialized defensive abilities of other units, and can be vulnerable when caught out alone and in the open."
